Promotion/Relegation Playoff [Jan 24, 26] 
Bangkok Metropolitan Administration bt Assumption Sriraja 

The Singha FA Cup was postponed because of lack of sponsorship, will be held 
next year but with reduced prize money.


14th Yamaha Thailand Cup

  [main inter-provincial competition]

Played between qualifiers from various regions.

Known regional representatives:   
Central region  - Samut Songkhram
Southern region - Ranong

